title: BRIEF-Alliancebernstein LP Says That AB Will Establish Its Corporate Headquarters In Nashville, Tennessee
text:
May 2, 2018 / 12:28 PM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Alliancebernstein LP Says That AB Will Establish Its Corporate Headquarters In Nashville, Tennessee Reuters Staff
May 2 (Reuters) - AllianceBernstein Holding LP:
* ALLIANCEBERNSTEIN L.P. SAYS THAT AB WILL ESTABLISH ITS CORPORATE HEADQUARTERS IN NASHVILLE, TENNESSEE - SEC FILING
* ALLIANCEBERNSTEIN LP-TO RELOCATE ABOUT 1,050 JOBS CURRENTLY LOCATED IN NEW YORK METRO AREA TO, NASHVILLE, TN; WILL BEGIN RELOCATING JOBS DURING 2018 Source text: [ bit.ly/2rfgmZY ] Further company coverage:
